# Emulation and File Formats

The project supports various ZX Spectrum file formats:

## Supported Formats
- Z80: Snapshot format (.z80 files)
- TAP: Tape format (.tap files)
- TZX: Advanced tape format (.tzx files)

## Emulation Components
- [firmware/src/Emulator/](mdc:firmware/src/Emulator/) - Core Z80 CPU and ZX Spectrum emulation
- [firmware/src/TZX/](mdc:firmware/src/TZX/) - TZX format handling
- [firmware/src/Screens/](mdc:firmware/src/Screens/) - User interface screens

## Interface
- [firmware/src/SerialInterface/](mdc:firmware/src/SerialInterface/) - Serial communication
- [firmware/src/Serial.cpp](mdc:firmware/src/Serial.cpp) - Serial port handling
